A set of codes for modeling and visualizing the dynamics of 
simple classical pendulum systems. 

single_pendulum_code_matlab/ 
- contains Matlab codes

single_pendulum_code_C_opengl/
- contains standalone C/C++ with OpenGl code

The OpenGL version has been tested on Linux with the free glut library. 
To compile, see the compile.sh script. 

Sergey Voronin, 2015.
